text: Quite a huge supermarket located at the basement of Tampines Hub. There are lots of items around the store and it is 24 hours which is pretty nice. There are also bento boxes at the entrance that you can buy. It's clean and well maintained and a lot of products on discounts. 👍 The self check out worked well too.
Big supermarket with good promotion from time to time. 24 hours.
Located in the basement level of Tampines Hub, the supermarket is very large and spacious. You can find a wide variety of items there. Make sure you have enough time for your shopping.
Very big, wide variey of food
